sequenceDiagram
    participant User as Data Scientist
    participant Browser as User Browser
    participant OAuth as OpenShift OAuth<br/>443/TCP HTTPS
    participant Dashboard as ODH Dashboard<br/>8443/TCP HTTPS<br/>OAuth Bearer
    participant K8sAPI as Kubernetes API<br/>6443/TCP HTTPS<br/>ServiceAccount Token
    participant NBCtrl as Notebook Controller<br/>Reconciler
    participant Gateway as Gateway API<br/>443/TCP HTTPS
    participant Notebook as Jupyter Notebook<br/>8888/TCP HTTPS
    participant S3 as S3 Storage<br/>443/TCP HTTPS<br/>AWS IAM
    participant KServe as KServe Controller<br/>Reconciler
    participant ModelCtrl as odh-model-controller<br/>Reconciler
    participant Predictor as Inference Pod<br/>8000/TCP HTTPS
    participant Prometheus as Prometheus<br/>Metrics scraping

    Note over User,Prometheus: Workflow 1: Notebook-Based Model Development and Deployment

    User->>Browser: Access Platform
    Browser->>OAuth: Authenticate<br/>OAuth 2.0/OIDC
    OAuth-->>Browser: Bearer Token
    Browser->>Dashboard: GET /<br/>Bearer Token
    Dashboard-->>Browser: Platform UI

    Browser->>Dashboard: Create Notebook CR<br/>POST /api/notebooks
    Dashboard->>K8sAPI: Create Notebook CR<br/>6443/HTTPS
    K8sAPI-->>NBCtrl: Watch Notification
    NBCtrl->>K8sAPI: Create StatefulSet + Service<br/>6443/HTTPS
    NBCtrl->>K8sAPI: Create HTTPRoute + NetworkPolicy<br/>6443/HTTPS
    K8sAPI-->>Gateway: HTTPRoute created
    K8sAPI-->>Notebook: Pod scheduled

    Browser->>Gateway: Access Jupyter<br/>443/HTTPS (OAuth)
    Gateway->>Notebook: Forward request<br/>8888/HTTP
    Notebook-->>Gateway: Jupyter UI
    Gateway-->>Browser: 200 OK

    Note over Notebook,S3: Model Development Phase
    Notebook->>Notebook: Train model locally
    Notebook->>S3: Save model artifacts<br/>PUT /bucket/model.pkl<br/>443/HTTPS (AWS SigV4)
    S3-->>Notebook: 200 OK

    Note over Notebook,Predictor: Model Deployment Phase
    Notebook->>K8sAPI: Create InferenceService CR<br/>6443/HTTPS
    K8sAPI-->>KServe: Watch Notification
    K8sAPI-->>ModelCtrl: Watch Notification

    KServe->>S3: Download model<br/>GET /bucket/model.pkl<br/>443/HTTPS
    S3-->>KServe: Model artifacts
    KServe->>K8sAPI: Create Deployment/Service<br/>6443/HTTPS
    K8sAPI-->>Predictor: Pod scheduled

    ModelCtrl->>K8sAPI: Create Route + ServiceMonitor<br/>6443/HTTPS
    K8sAPI-->>Prometheus: ServiceMonitor created

    Note over User,Predictor: Inference Phase
    Browser->>Predictor: POST /v1/models/model:predict<br/>443/HTTPS<br/>JSON payload
    Predictor->>Predictor: Run inference
    Predictor-->>Browser: Prediction result

    Prometheus->>Predictor: GET /metrics<br/>Scrape metrics
    Predictor-->>Prometheus: Prometheus metrics
